    "en": {
      "title": "10 lakh people register for fuel license",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Energy said that 10 lakh people have registered for the 'National Fuel Licence' as of today (17) afternoon.",
        "The ministry further said that these ten lakh people have registered their vehicles within a day of introducing the telephone application for registration to this 'National Fuel Licence'."
